            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>截至台北時間02日00:00，<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/GBPJPY\">英鎊/日元</a>上漲1.62點漲幅達0.77%，暫報211.42點。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li>近 1 月：-0.29%</li><li>近 1 週：-1.39%</li><li>近 3 月：-0.58%</li><li>近 6 月：+5.57%</li><li>今年以來：-0.59%</li></ul></section><section><p><em><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/GBPJPY\">英鎊/日元</a>近90天正相關的前3貨幣對</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li> <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>相關性0.83，本日上漲0.46%        </li> <li> <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/audusd\">澳元</a>/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>相關性0.73，本日上漲0.58%        </li> <li>            瑞郎/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/jpyusd\">日元</a>相關性0.69，本日上漲0.83%        </li> </ul></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/GBPJPY\">英鎊/日元</a>近90天負相關的前3貨幣對</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li> <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/gbpusd\">英鎊</a>相關性-0.37，本日上漲0.28%        </li> <li> <a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/eurusd\">歐元</a>/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/audusd\">澳元</a>相關性-0.26，本日上漲0.1%        </li> <li>            美元/<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/forex/detail/zarusd\">南非蘭特</a>相關性-0.16，本日上漲0.73%        </li> </ul></section></main>",
